name: Karasu
description:
"Perched above the carnage is the Karasu, black as night against the inky sky. Its piercing eyes flit from side to side, landing on its prey below. It lets out a cry that rattles the leaves and strikes fear through the hearts of every living creature below" - Sykcolo / AI

Karasu by @Sykcoloart

Taking something that most would consider ugly or repulsive and showing it in a different way that transforms it into something uniquely beautiful is the main passion behind this project that I called Metamorphoses.

This artwork is created using generative techniques to mutate and deconstruct a micrograph of a crow feather. 

Learn about the inspiration, story and techniques behind this project on my website: https://www.sykcolo.com/blog-1/the-metamorphoses-collection
